text: Saint-Aubin-le-Guichard was a commune in Normandy in the Eure department in north France. On 1 January 2016, it became part of the new commune, Mesnil-en- Ouche.Arrêté préfectoral 9 December 2015 == References == Category:Former communes in France Category:Communes in Eure
title: Saint-Aubin-le-Guichard
